<div class="answer-head">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730"
class="zm-item-link-avatar"
href="/people/kaiserwang730">
<img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="65">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$fan-qie-de-xiang-jiao" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/fan-qie-de-xiang-jiao" class="zg-link" title="番茄的香蕉">番茄的香蕉</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$lei-ling-95" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/lei-ling-95" class="zg-link" title="雷零">雷零</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$li-an-nuo-92-61" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/li-an-nuo-92-61" class="zg-link" title="李安娜">李安娜</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2203087" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">如何蹲起不难，西洋有力士深蹲博士，身体力行总结出了很多有用的心得：<br><br><a href="http://bbs.hupu.com/8218814.html" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">深蹲博士的理论集锦zt非常好的训练学习资料，大家请看看吧！<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br><a href="http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_706e92a901019n6z.html" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">深蹲博士谈关于深蹲的谎言与真相（一）（二）<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br><br>也有仁人志士指出他存在的的问题：<br><a href="http://safeguarddo.blog.163.com/blog/static/11151310120094280845412/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">与深蹲博士探讨实用性训练<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br><br>难就难在优雅上。<br><br>老话讲工夫在诗外，深蹲还是那个深蹲，我觉得要做到优雅，需要考虑的因素就很多。<br><br>灯光、音效这些都是必备的。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/f4b6271bea4383cacb30da0e69ea6738_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="663" data-rawheight="436" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="663" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/f4b6271bea4383cacb30da0e69ea6738_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="663" data-rawheight="436" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="663" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/f4b6271bea4383cacb30da0e69ea6738_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/f4b6271bea4383cacb30da0e69ea6738_b.jpg"><br>红色的灯光让人产生不好的联想，黄色的灯光使人感到温暖；而蓝色的灯光静谧幽深，让我有种要被吸进去了的感觉。<br><br>音效也很重要，激昂、奋进的乐曲使蹲者更有斗志，在力量与节奏中中展现优雅。<br>如果还有无数挥舞着荧光棒的观众那就更完美了。<br><br>优雅是一种美学欣赏，你需要一些陪衬，比如到健身房去报名之前先看一圈，如果这里的会员都比自己高太多，则容易产生自卑畏惧心理。比如我作为男性，如果运动场所全是肌肉男反而我很不自在，就是周围的人跟我差不多甚至还弱一些的时候我比较容易找到运动的状态。<br><br>比如明星开演唱会总要有伴舞，他们的身材相貌都不如主角，也不给他们追光，因此才衬托出天后的优雅。服装当然也是需要考究的，要适合做大幅度运动，又能显出自己的身材为佳。<br><br>看那小蓝帽，云髻峨峨，修眉联娟。<br>观这俏短裙，瓌姿艳逸，仪静体闲。<br>好一个，柔情绰态，媚于语言。奇服旷世，骨像应图。<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/d5a39722b84b0acb30b4526e54a5db86_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="569" data-rawheight="434" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="569" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/d5a39722b84b0acb30b4526e54a5db86_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="569" data-rawheight="434" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="569" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/d5a39722b84b0acb30b4526e54a5db86_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/d5a39722b84b0acb30b4526e54a5db86_b.jpg"><br>正式开始深蹲之前注意做热身运动，一来是为安全计，防止关节扭伤；二来优雅需要铺垫，就像故事的高潮总在后头，秀出你的事业线，先把观众的眼球吸引过来，给他们一种期待会使优雅倍增。<br><br>披罗衣之璀粲兮，珥瑶碧之华琚。戴金翠之首饰，缀明珠以耀躯。<br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/21053ee7c5525e20d8611ac32653b7fd_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="570" data-rawheight="434" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="570" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/21053ee7c5525e20d8611ac32653b7fd_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="570" data-rawheight="434" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="570" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/21053ee7c5525e20d8611ac32653b7fd_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/21053ee7c5525e20d8611ac32653b7fd_b.jpg"><br>但是不要给他们准备的时间，节奏到了说蹲就蹲，其形也，翩若惊鸿，婉若游龙。<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/7c10f6eabf20c1f992d24708f96da2e2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="120" data-rawheight="233" class="content_image" width="120"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="120" data-rawheight="233" class="content_image lazy" width="120" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/7c10f6eabf20c1f992d24708f96da2e2_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/b9ed1fef0b9eb2a5bb540b92f82a6a09_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="120" data-rawheight="204" class="content_image" width="120"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="120" data-rawheight="204" class="content_image lazy" width="120" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/b9ed1fef0b9eb2a5bb540b92f82a6a09_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/162a856d0803b51f9a7e7507efda55f8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="120" data-rawheight="158" class="content_image" width="120"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="120" data-rawheight="158" class="content_image lazy" width="120" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/162a856d0803b51f9a7e7507efda55f8_b.jpg"><br>蹲下不要马上起来，保持姿态，面向观众，肩若削成，腰如约素。延颈秀项，皓质呈露。<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/2bb8c64b0c0509a9b0331a8f7e84ff3b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="545" data-rawheight="429" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="545" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/2bb8c64b0c0509a9b0331a8f7e84ff3b_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="545" data-rawheight="429" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="545" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/2bb8c64b0c0509a9b0331a8f7e84ff3b_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/2bb8c64b0c0509a9b0331a8f7e84ff3b_b.jpg"><br>哎，好，起~要富有动感，蹲如处子，起如脱兔，竦轻躯以鹤立，若将飞而未翔。<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/f6fc9973f7bde81210ed08df639babef_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="564" data-rawheight="426" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="564" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/f6fc9973f7bde81210ed08df639babef_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="564" data-rawheight="426" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="564" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/f6fc9973f7bde81210ed08df639babef_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/f6fc9973f7bde81210ed08df639babef_b.jpg"><br>好起得很成功，然后活动一下筋骨，调整呼吸，特别是负重蹲起这点很重要。活动的这一下也是展示优雅的大好时机，最好能自己设计一套富有特色的动作，微幽兰之芳蔼兮，步踟蹰于山隅。于是忽焉纵体，以遨以嬉。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/a8c64ab734a49d5ba669202be4ccd974_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="564" data-rawheight="431" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="564" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/a8c64ab734a49d5ba669202be4ccd974_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="564" data-rawheight="431" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="564" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/a8c64ab734a49d5ba669202be4ccd974_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/a8c64ab734a49d5ba669202be4ccd974_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/8278db6121364dad8d776dd47de19155_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="567" data-rawheight="428" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="567" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/8278db6121364dad8d776dd47de19155_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="567" data-rawheight="428" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="567" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/8278db6121364dad8d776dd47de19155_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/8278db6121364dad8d776dd47de19155_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/43d8b733e177fba0351cc5b017e8f249_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="565" data-rawheight="429" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="565" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/43d8b733e177fba0351cc5b017e8f249_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="565" data-rawheight="429" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="565" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/43d8b733e177fba0351cc5b017e8f249_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/43d8b733e177fba0351cc5b017e8f249_b.jpg"><br>注意观察观众的反应，对于那些不懂得欣赏优雅的人，要无情的打击，再踏上一万只脚。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/e3e7f4b0afd99ad56b3aaa063acad528_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="559" data-rawheight="424" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="559" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/e3e7f4b0afd99ad56b3aaa063acad528_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="559" data-rawheight="424" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="559" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/e3e7f4b0afd99ad56b3aaa063acad528_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/e3e7f4b0afd99ad56b3aaa063acad528_b.jpg"><br>优雅是一种姿态，不仅是肢体，更是自信的表现。在蹲起的过程中，放松活力，保持微笑，丹唇外朗，皓齿内鲜。明眸善睐，靥辅承权。<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/37e46ea79c0487aca28b735e8fda805b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="571" data-rawheight="432" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="571" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/37e46ea79c0487aca28b735e8fda805b_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="571" data-rawheight="432" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="571" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/37e46ea79c0487aca28b735e8fda805b_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/37e46ea79c0487aca28b735e8fda805b_b.jpg"><br>这个运动要分组进行，短暂的休息完后，再来一组：<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/e3b3c79cefd165f4ff1a1650bcbf3792_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="557" data-rawheight="432" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="557" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/e3b3c79cefd165f4ff1a1650bcbf3792_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="557" data-rawheight="432" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="557" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/e3b3c79cefd165f4ff1a1650bcbf3792_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/e3b3c79cefd165f4ff1a1650bcbf3792_b.jpg"><br>力量训练上来之后可以尝试一下单腿的，这个一般人可真来不了。<br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/f748fdae48daaa14ebfaddf4af4aef61_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="573" data-rawheight="425" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="573" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/f748fdae48daaa14ebfaddf4af4aef61_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="573" data-rawheight="425" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="573" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/f748fdae48daaa14ebfaddf4af4aef61_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/f748fdae48daaa14ebfaddf4af4aef61_b.jpg"><br>一组完成之后，再来放松一下，仿佛兮若轻云之蔽月，飘飖兮若流风之回雪。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/143924b5d6af5aa270b85f217419923c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="524" data-rawheight="434" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="524" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/143924b5d6af5aa270b85f217419923c_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="524" data-rawheight="434" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="524" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/143924b5d6af5aa270b85f217419923c_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/143924b5d6af5aa270b85f217419923c_b.jpg"><br><br>体迅飞凫，飘忽若神。凌波微步，罗袜生尘。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/fd5f1104f456a8b7bd89a313f80e6f1c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="541" data-rawheight="434" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="541" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/fd5f1104f456a8b7bd89a313f80e6f1c_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="541" data-rawheight="434" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="541" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/fd5f1104f456a8b7bd89a313f80e6f1c_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/fd5f1104f456a8b7bd89a313f80e6f1c_b.jpg"><br>嗯，按照这个节奏来就差不多了，如果深蹲练习的足够优雅了，我们还有其他的大招没有放。不过那就超脱蹲起的范围了，我们下次再谈噜。


</div>

